%% 3.2.13 View Order Detail — sequence
%% GET /api/Order/Get/{id}
%% BR60: PAID orders are read-only — no edits from app

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Guardian as Guardian
    participant App as Mobile App
    participant OC as OrderController
    participant OS as OrderService
    participant Repo as IRepository Order
    participant DB as SQL Server

    Guardian->>App: Tap order card
    App->>OC: GET /api/Order/Get/{id} Bearer
    OC->>OS: GetOrderByIdAsync
    OS->>Repo: Include guardian, student, package, route...
    Repo->>DB: SELECT
    OS-->>OC: OrderDto
    OC-->>App: 200 OK — read-only invoice
